divs: Sighting DetailsI was on AOL today, and one of the pages had a GE "Ecomagination" long commercial running. In the scene where the young man is on the beach and a parasail is floating behind him in the background, a white cigar shaped object moves quickly right to left in the background. The particular scene only lasts about five seconds, and the object appears on screen for about one second.
Summary: A UFO appears in the background of a GE Ecomagination commercial
